Script to generate extended data fig. 8:
f1_draw_curve_of_heatwave_days_newregion_reg51new21_revNat.m

Data needed for this script are available from the Zenodo repository (link available in home directory of this project)
"region_heatwave_proportion.zip" - ERA5 heatwave proportion data
"CESM_LENS2_region_heatwave_proportion.zip" - CESM large ensemble heatwave proportion data
"region_all_fire_xth2.zip" - regional fire data from satellite
